# Main CSS Classes

| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.header` | Main header container |
| `.main-menu` | Navigation menu |
| `.icons` | Icon wrapper |
| `.icon-box` | Cart icon container |
| `.badge` | Notification badge |
| `.home-menu` | Active menu item |

